name: ChimeraMix
description:
This mix is more focused on (un)realistic creatures/monsters, merging concepts, but seems to be a quite versatile/creative base model. Can be merged with more specific models to steer its direction.

Check out WyvernMix for realistic portraits, SuccubusMix for more nsfw portraits, or HydraMix which tries to balance all of these.

Model comparisons (First column: WyvernV9, then ChimeraV4, ChimeraV3, HydraV1)
at 896x1152

modelVersions.description: Bringing back some realistic portrait support, while trying to retain the concepts and flexibility.

further adjustments, toned back a bit on realism and faces, HydraMix is now better in that sense.

wereanimals might be a bit too strong in this one, but it brought better coherency

also added the pokemerge lora, so it might have better creativity in creating new creatures
